I not have laptop

Pada tanggal 11 Feb 2018 4.14 PM, "ericwhiteau" <notifications@github.com>
menulis:

Hi there,
I had the same problem and attempted to follow the above workaround.
(without success)

But then thinking about the original error. "Version miss match with
Tensorflow"

Easy solution which worked for me.

Verify the version of Tensorflow used on the Laptop to build 1.5.0

Set same version in Android build. Slap forehead....

dependencies {
compile 'org.tensorflow:tensorflow-android:1.5.0'
}

done ....

—
